2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses tracking of event cameras in a panoramic setting with three degrees of freedom, which is relevant to robotics applications. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper may involve machine learning techniques for camera tracking and mapping. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper may involve AI techniques for camera tracking and mapping. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may involve control systems for camera tracking and mapping.
